Name: Unfiltered by Samdish (and a fantastic team)
Description:
If you like our work, you can become an active member of the unfiltered community here: https://unfilteredhq.com/

We create videos that are quite literally " unfiltered" at their core. I'm a curious citizen, trying to explore the democratic fabric of my country by interviewing various politicians, celebrities, gatecrashing election rallies, and reporting from the ground. I, along with 3 of my colleagues decided to quit our stable jobs and start something of our own. We're here to create amazing content and break the internet every now and then.
